# Surge 5 RULE-SET (DOMAIN-SUFFIX rules)
# Target Policy: DIRECT
# Tested style: Surge 5 iOS (5.17.1)
#
# Usage:
#   [Rule]
#   RULE-SET,https://your-domain-or-raw-link/china.list,DIRECT
#
# Notes:
# - This file is intentionally "broad" for CN ecosystems (Alibaba/Tencent/Baidu/ByteDance/etc.).
# - Put your PROXY rule-sets (e.g., github.list) ABOVE this in Surge rules order.
# - For the most complete CN-direct behavior, also add: GEOIP,CN,DIRECT (see below).

# --- Mainland China TLDs ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cn
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,xn--fiqs8s      # 中国
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,xn--55qx5d      # 公司
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,xn--io0a7i      # 网络

# --- Alibaba / Ant / Aliyun / Taobao / Tmall / CDN ---
